d.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> How much Stealth is too much?</span><hr size=1> I spent a lot of the weekend fooling around in various Midgard keeps, beginning to look at the feasibility of actually stealing relics.<br><br>I'm L41 with 40 Stealth (36 + 4) and this is adequate to sneak around most of an enemy keep.  It's not enough however to gain access to any of the vital spots (gatehouse, relic tower, keep lord, etc.)<br><br>I can get within about a horse length of any normal guard before I'm detected.  Distraction lets me sneak by even closer, once the guard is turned in the other direction.<br><br>Masters of Runes however detect me at a far greater range, and they guard all of the important locations.  I actually need to get quite close to them, under a horse length, to get to anything significant.<br><br>So I'm wondering if 50 adjusted stealth is going to be enough to actually attempt a theft.  I'm considering going to 50 natural stealth in order to boost my overall stealth above 60.<br><br>Does anybody know what the stealth requirement is to avoid being detected by a Master of Runes? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uravnnevermoor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravn Nevermoor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 9:49:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much Stealth is too much?</span><hr size=1> I would stop investing points at 36-40, I've been playing my inf since the day DAoC came out and I had no one else to rely on for advice, So, I went full 50 spec in stealth. Well, needless to say, I see people who I know have 36 base spec stealth at the same time they see me. In Mythic's version of Math 36 is equal to 50. <p>Ravn Nevermoor<Br>50 infiltrator<Br>Aeonian Prophecy</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uravnnevermoor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravn Nevermoor</A> at: 7/8/02 9:50:46 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ukeybaud.showPublicProfile?language=EN>keybaud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 9:56:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much Stealth is too much?</span><hr size=1> As far as i can tell, the high level guards with range don't detect you, you just come into range and get blown to pieces. I think your stealth is irrelevant.<br><br>Snee <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uaureliuscov.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aurelius CoV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 10:14:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much Stealth is too much?</span><hr size=1> Attempting a theft is moot. It WONT happen since all relic keep doors have been upgraded to lvl 10. Maybe if you and 7 friends have a couple months to waste (the first theft took 8 hours on a level 1 door) *and* noone in that realm ever strolls through or logs in a mule to look around..... I think you lose stealth arming seige weapons now too, so you will die before firing the ram.<br><br>Its a pipe dream that will never happen again. Kudos to the guys who did it though :)<br><br>50+ stealth does nothing for you.<br><br>Those new uber guards are like lvl 65 or something, they will pick up 50s with max stealth relatively closely also. <p><center><br>"I am still learning" <br>- Michelangelo</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ushadowerbdc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ShadowerBDC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 11:40:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much Stealth is too much?</span><hr size=1> It's my understanding that the guards in the portal and border keeps are the ones with Detect Hidden.  The guards in relic and other frontier keeps don't have detect hidden, they just detect normally as a Lxx character would.<br><br>What I was wondering was whether getting stealth into the mid-60's would protect as well against them as having stealth at 50 does against non-Detect Hidden 50 PC's. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uzanthiathenightshade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ZanthiatheNightshade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 3:02:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ..moot question</span><hr size=1> Even if you can take all the doors down and reach the top of the relic keep, grabbing a relic unstealths you. Also, while holding a relic, you cannot stealth. That means you and your rogue friends will have to climb down the relic tower, up the stairs and out of the outter wall AND run all the way down the hill without being killed. Against relic keep guards? I have my doubts about 50 level 50 infiltrators being able to pull it off. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/ubrandynaquilius.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brandyn Aquilius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 5:51:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ..moot question</span><hr size=1> What Zanth said.  AND the Guards will NOT stop chasing you until they are dead.  You can't just &quot;steal&quot; a relic.  Unfortunately. <p>-Aurra Sing-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/umelanu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melanu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/8/02 10:38:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3707.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ..moot question</span><hr size=1> nevermind<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/umelanu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melanu</A> at: 7/8/02 10:45:14 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td 